NK010(tha)017:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las dam can nye bar bsnyen
NK010(tha)017:1: pa'i phrin las smad las kyi srog shing zhes bya
NK010(tha)017:2: ba bzhugs / dpal chen badz+ra ku m+aa ra la na ma /
NK010(tha)017:3: 'dir rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa smad las kyi dang po dam can nye bar bsnyen pa ni /
NK010(tha)017:5: bsgrubs na chags pa'i srung ma ni //
NK010(tha)017:6: bcu gnyis dag tu shes pa la //
NK010(tha)017:7: shwa na mu kha lcags spyang mo //
NK010(tha)017:8: shwa na mu kha lcags khyi mo //
NK010(tha)017:9: sri la mu kha zags 'phar ma //
NK010(tha)017:10: sri la mu kha zags wa mo //
NK010(tha)017:11: sa bdag bzhi ni 'grub par nges //
NK010(tha)017:12: bdag nyid bzhi ni dpyid dbyar dang //
NK010(tha)017:13: ston dgun bzhi yi rgyal mo ste //
NK010(tha)017:14: bzhi tshan gsum po dag tu ni //
NK010(tha)017:15: bsten cing ba ling sbyin par bya //
NK010(tha)017:16: de la dngos grub myur bar 'ong //
NK010(tha)017:22: nyams pa bdun po bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)017:23: drag po'i dus gzung yo byad gsog /
NK010(tha)017:24: rtsa ba'i man+dala lho nub tu //
NK010(tha)017:25: bse byang sbrag ma'i man+dala ni //
NK010(tha)017:26: dbus su gru gsum mthur du bru //
NK010(tha)017:27: phyi rim zla gam mu khyud bca' //
NK010(tha)017:29: de yi phyi rol gru chad bzhir //
NK010(tha)017:30: gru gsum mthing nag re re bya //
NK010(tha)017:32: dam can gnas pa'i gru gsum bzhi //
NK010(tha)017:33: phyogs bzhi dag tu nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)017:34: re rer thod chen re re la //
NK010(tha)017:35: ling+ga bcas pa der bcug la //
NK010(tha)017:36: rdzas rnams nges par tshogs par gsog /
NK010(tha)017:37: lcags phur dbus su dgod par bya //
NK010(tha)017:38: mi bzad phur pa drug rnams ni //
NK010(tha)017:39: gru gsum drug la shes par bya //
NK010(tha)017:40: dam can ma lus phur pa dang //
NK010(tha)017:41: ming po gsum 'dus phur pa gcig /
NK010(tha)017:42: phyogs bzhi dag tu legs par dgod //
NK010(tha)017:43: ces pa las 'khor lo drug ni rtsibs drug dang /
NK010(tha)017:44: gru gsum drug ni rtsibs mchan du bri bar bya la /
NK010(tha)017:45: de yang brub khung la brten nas dam can nye
NK010(tha)017:46: bar bsnyen pa ni mtshan ma 'byin pa'i las yin
NK010(tha)017:47: pas dmigs pa'i rten ling+ga bca' ba'i tshul /
NK010(tha)017:48: shing shun ro ras dag la ni //
NK010(tha)017:50: dur khrod smyu gu khrag chen gyi //
NK010(tha)017:51: zhe sdang bcas pa'i sems kyis bris //
NK010(tha)017:52: 'khor lo rtsibs drug bcas pa la //
NK010(tha)017:53: spyi bor dang k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)017:54: snying gar mig dang dpral bar rus //
NK010(tha)017:55: g.yas su h+aum la g.yon du phata //
NK010(tha)017:56: m+aa ra ya ni 'doms su ste //
NK010(tha)017:57: drug la sngags drug bcas pa'o //
NK010(tha)017:58: srog la 'dren pa'i snying po rnams //
NK010(tha)017:59: mtshams la 'phyang drug nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)017:60: thams cad 'dus pas mtha' ma bskor //
NK010(tha)017:61: zhes pas 'khor lo rtsibs drug gi lto bar ling+ga dang /
NK010(tha)017:62: rtsibs drug la mgo thog nas brtsams te ha sa ya ra sogs gab pa'i sngags drug /
NK010(tha)017:63: rtsibs mchan drug la gdags pa'i 'phyong drug /
NK010(tha)017:64: gnad yig tu bstan pa'i thams cad 'dus pa'i ri rab kyis mtha' bskor /
NK010(tha)017:65: zag rdzas la sogs byugs pa rabs chad kyi thod
NK010(tha)017:66: par stsal la dbus kyi brub khung du bcug pa'i
NK010(tha)017:67: snyig gar bsnyen phur gzug cing kha khyer rtsang gis
NK010(tha)017:68: bskor / de'i steng du sku gsung thugs kyi brten bcas nas gzir ba'i tshul /
NK010(tha)017:69: sba mkhar tshig gsum dag la yang //
NK010(tha)017:70: bse byang snying po bcas pa gdags //
NK010(tha)017:71: bse byang nag po snying por bcas //
NK010(tha)017:72: de 'og gnyis la gdags par bya //
NK010(tha)017:73: bse byang dkar po snying por bcas //
NK010(tha)017:74: de yi 'og tu shes par bya //
NK010(tha)017:75: de 'og bse mo nag mo dang //
NK010(tha)017:76: sho na'i sku dang snying por bcas //
NK010(tha)017:77: sba tshigs bzhi pa dag la'o //
NK010(tha)017:78: tha mar ling+ga skud par gdags //
NK010(tha)017:79: man+dala nang du sba mkhar gyis //
NK010(tha)017:81: zhes pa ltar sku'i rten bse'i byang bu la ma mo bcu gnyis kyi nal bu dang /
NK010(tha)017:84: nya'i pags pa las byas pa'i bse grub na mchog yin no //
NK010(tha)017:86: sku gtor bzlog tu bstan pa'i bskul byang gi mngon rtogs ltar ram /
NK010(tha)017:88: dam can ma ni 'di lta ste //
NK010(tha)017:89: nag mo nag la bswe mo dmar //
NK010(tha)017:90: sho na dkar ldem ming po ser //
NK010(tha)017:91: zhal gcig phyag gnyis lcags kyu phur //
NK010(tha)017:92: rangs pa rnams la chibs med do //
NK010(tha)017:94: chibs sam yang na rkyang pa ste //
NK010(tha)017:95: rang rang phyag mtshan phur pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)017:98: rgyal po dkar po ging dkar phur //
NK010(tha)017:99: ma h+aa k+aa la mdog nag ste //
NK010(tha)017:100: be con phur bu rgyan dang ldan //
NK010(tha)017:101: bswe yi skyes bu dmar po 'jigs //
NK010(tha)017:102: bse mda' bse gzhu phur pa 'dril //
NK010(tha)017:103: chibs sam yang na rkyang pa ste //
NK010(tha)017:104: zhes pa ltar gyis rgyab tu so so'i gsung gi
NK010(tha)017:105: snying po sngags byang dang bcas pa bris nas rab
NK010(tha)017:106: tu gnas pa thugs kyi rten sba lcag tshigs gsum
NK010(tha)017:107: pa'i lhu dang por thabs shes kyi dbang las bswe'i
NK010(tha)017:108: skyes bu / gnyis par lcags kyi skyes bu /
NK010(tha)017:109: gsum par dung gi skyes bu /
NK010(tha)017:110: bzhi par ma mo bcu gnyis po gdags pa brub
NK010(tha)017:111: khung gi steng du btsugs pa ling+ga dang srad bus
NK010(tha)017:112: sbrel / thod pa mtshan ngan bzhi'i nang du ming
NK010(tha)017:113: rus dang ldan pa'i nya bo re bcug la dam
NK010(tha)017:114: can gsum dang ming po gsum 'dus kyi phur pa
NK010(tha)017:115: gzir ba so so'i lha gnas su bkod /
NK010(tha)017:116: dam can rnam gsum mthun pa'i rdzas //
NK010(tha)017:117: thod pa bcu gnyis yang na gsum //
NK010(tha)017:118: de ru thun gyi sbyor ba bya //
NK010(tha)017:119: gtor ma la sogs nges par bsag /
NK010(tha)017:121: drag po'i dam rdzas mang po rnams //
NK010(tha)017:122: thod pa tshal bu'i nang du gsog /
NK010(tha)017:123: ces pa ltar so so'i thun rdzas gnad yig ltar dang /
NK010(tha)017:125: bswe yi lha mo'i rdzas rnams ni //
NK010(tha)017:126: 'o ma zhag dang mar khu dang //
NK010(tha)017:127: sbrang rtsi dang ni chang rnams so //
NK010(tha)017:129: de bzhin sho na mu kha'i yang //
NK010(tha)017:130: khyi thod wa thod spyang thod dang //
NK010(tha)017:131: 'phar ba'i thod pa de bzhin te //
NK010(tha)017:132: de yi nang du rdzas bsag pa //
NK010(tha)017:133: khrag sna stong dang sha sna stong //
NK010(tha)017:134: snying sna stong dang rkang sna stong //
NK010(tha)017:135: sho na la sogs rdzas su bzhag /
NK010(tha)017:136: re ma ti yi rdzas rnams kyang //
NK010(tha)017:137: nal bu'i sha la sogs pa ste //
NK010(tha)017:138: mi thod dang bse phor nang du /
NK010(tha)017:139: du ma nyid du bsag par bya //
NK010(tha)017:140: rkang chen dung dang zhing chen dang //
NK010(tha)017:142: mtshon cha drug kyang bsag par bya //
NK010(tha)017:151: khrag sna tshogs bse'i skyes bu la'o //
NK010(tha)017:154: rta nag gi rmig pa g.yas /
NK010(tha)017:158: phur pa nag po mgon po la'o //
NK010(tha)017:163: phur pa dkar po la sogs pa rgyal po'am dung mi skyes bu'i mthun rdzas so //
NK010(tha)017:164: de bzhin du sman raka gtor gsum /
NK010(tha)017:165: thugs dam bskang ba'i dam rdzas rnams sgo thams cad nas tshogs par bya'o //
NK010(tha)017:167: dang po rtsa ba'i lha gsum ni /
NK010(tha)017:168: gzhung bzhin legs par bskyed pa yin //
NK010(tha)017:169: dbang bskur byin dbab spyan drang bya //
NK010(tha)017:170: mchod cing bstod de smon lam gdab //
NK010(tha)017:171: ces thog mar yi dam gyi mngon rtogs bzlas pa'i bar bya'o //
NK010(tha)017:172: gnyis pa dam can nye bar bsnyen pa la gsum /
NK010(tha)017:173: bzhi snying dril nas 'bod pa bsnyen pa /
NK010(tha)017:174: gnad la dbab nas rbad pa bsgrub pa /
NK010(tha)017:175: thun du bsgrub nas bsad pa las sbyor las /
NK010(tha)017:176: dang po'i don du 'dzab kha dbye ba ni /
NK010(tha)017:178: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)017:179: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)017:180: phung po rdo rjer gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)017:181: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)017:183: sku gsung thugs kyi rten rnams dam can dngos kyi snang char gsal ba ste /
NK010(tha)017:184: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hohka tam
NK010(tha)017:185: ka ye dza ye bi dza ye a tsi te
NK010(tha)017:187: ma ra sa na pra ma rta na ye sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:189: bdag nyid yi dam du gsal ba'i thugs ka'i 'od
NK010(tha)017:190: zer gyis dam can rnams kyi srog snying phrogs pas
NK010(tha)017:191: ci bcol ba'i las nyan par bsam mo //
NK010(tha)017:193: bar bar mchod bstod gnad la dbab //
NK010(tha)017:194: rang rang dam rdzas legs par btab //
NK010(tha)017:198: badz+ra kro d+ha tsit+ta ma h+aa l+ai shu ra shu ra /
NK010(tha)017:199: khyi ra khing g+ha d+ha ra ni /
NK010(tha)017:200: shu la tsi p+aa ra shu pa ra ni /
NK010(tha)017:201: yo ga shud+d+ha tsit+ta ma ra li /
NK010(tha)017:202: kro d+ha yo gi n+ai badz+ra /
NK010(tha)017:204: sha sha ni dzahdzahi dam ba lim ta p+au tsa kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)017:205: zhes lan bdun gyis bsngo zhing /
NK010(tha)017:208: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)017:209: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)017:211: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)017:212: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par gyis //
NK010(tha)017:214: rten la 'od zer gyi d+r+wa bas bcing /
NK010(tha)017:215: thun mthar tshogs kyi mchod pa dang bskang ba ci nus bya /
NK010(tha)017:216: cho ga'i rjes cho ga gi mthar nyal ba'i rnal 'byor la 'jug /
NK010(tha)017:217: rtags mtshan byung nas dngos grub ni //
NK010(tha)017:218: rab tu blang bar shes par bya //
NK010(tha)017:220: bsnyen tshad grangs nges ma bshad cing //
NK010(tha)017:224: tha ma nyams dang rtags su bshad //
NK010(tha)017:226: rtags mtshan tha ma dang nyams rmi lam gsum du
NK010(tha)017:227: gnad yig ltar gyi don 'du ba'i rtags mthong ba'am
NK010(tha)017:228: / bzlas pa 'bum phrag gcig la las rung du
NK010(tha)017:229: byas pa la 'bod rbad bsad gsum gyi dang po'i
NK010(tha)017:230: phur pa rang skad la dril te bzlas pa'i bsnyen
NK010(tha)017:231: / pa zhes bya'o // gnyis pa rbad pa'i las sam bsgrub pa ni /
NK010(tha)017:232: las sngags khong khrar sdeb pa'i man ngag la brten
NK010(tha)017:233: nas dam can las la bkol bas dgra bo'i bla
NK010(tha)017:234: 'gugs pa ste / drag sngags drug pa dam can dang //
NK010(tha)017:235: las sngags thams cad gong gi bar //
NK010(tha)017:236: man ngag rim pa shes pa yi //
NK010(tha)017:237: bzlas pa byas pas bla khugs 'gyur //
NK010(tha)017:239: dmar chen sbreng la dam can bskul //
NK010(tha)017:240: gab pa'i sngags kyis rab byas la //
NK010(tha)017:241: dam can mang pos dgra bo dgug /
NK010(tha)017:242: ming po'i bla 'gugs sngags kyis so //
NK010(tha)017:243: shes pa bstim pa yang yang ngo //
NK010(tha)017:244: zhes pas gtor ma la dmar chen sbrengs shing dam can gyi bskul ba rgyas pa'am /
NK010(tha)017:247: bstan par dgra 'dre byung ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)017:248: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)017:249: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)017:250: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)017:251: dregs pa mang po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)017:252: khyed kyis mthu rtsal rab tu dbyung //
NK010(tha)017:253: sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK010(tha)017:254: dkon mchog sku dgra dben rtsa 'joms //
NK010(tha)017:255: chos khrims 'dral dang slob dpon dgra //
NK010(tha)017:257: bsad dang dbab dang nad ngan gyis //
NK010(tha)017:258: ji nas brlag par khyod kyis gyis //
NK010(tha)017:259: nga ni khrag 'thung he ru ka /
NK010(tha)017:260: khyod kyi snying khrag nga la yod //
NK010(tha)017:261: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)017:262: khyod kyi 'das par gyur na ni //
NK010(tha)017:263: khro bo stobs chen he ru kas //
NK010(tha)017:264: mgo bo rdo rjes tshal par 'gas //
NK010(tha)017:265: de bas bka' las ma 'da' zhig /
NK010(tha)017:269: nyin mo gtor la nub mo dril //
NK010(tha)017:270: gang bab dus su shes par bya //
NK010(tha)017:271: zhes pas nyin mo gtor te bzlas pa ni /
NK010(tha)017:272: thun bzhi'i dang po la sho na ma rbad pa ni /
NK010(tha)017:273: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka tam ka ye che ge mo la b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK010(tha)017:274: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:275: gnyis pa la bswe mo rbad pa /
NK010(tha)017:276: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh dza
NK010(tha)017:277: ye bi dza ye che ge mo la b+h+yo b+h+yo
NK010(tha)017:278: / sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:279: gsum pa la re ma ti /
NK010(tha)017:280: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh a
NK010(tha)017:281: tsi te a pa ra tsit+ta che ge mo la
NK010(tha)017:282: b+h+yo b+h+yo / sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:284: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ma
NK010(tha)017:285: ra se na pra ma rta na ye che mo
NK010(tha)017:286: la b+h+yo b+h+yo / sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:288: nub mo dril te bzla ba ni /
NK010(tha)017:289: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka
NK010(tha)017:290: tam ka ye dza ye bi dza ye a tsi
NK010(tha)017:291: te a pa ra tsi ta /
NK010(tha)017:292: ma ra sa na pra marta na ye che ge
NK010(tha)017:293: mo m+aa ra ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata
NK010(tha)017:295: nyin nub gang la'ang bar bar du dam can gyi bskul bya /
NK010(tha)017:297: thod pa lcags mkhar sgo med du //
NK010(tha)017:298: dgra bo nges par gsal ming gsal //
NK010(tha)017:300: de yi shes pa la dgug pa dang //
NK010(tha)017:301: drag sngags bzhi yi sbyor ba bya //
NK010(tha)017:302: pho nya sngags dang ting 'dzin gsum //
NK010(tha)017:303: bran dang pho nya bka' nyan gyis //
NK010(tha)017:304: shes pa nges par dgug par bya //
NK010(tha)017:305: ming po sring mo'i dgug sngags sam //
NK010(tha)017:306: yang na ming po'i drag sngags so //
NK010(tha)017:307: ting 'dzin ri dwags sha bkye bzhin //
NK010(tha)017:308: ma khugs bar du nges par sbyar //
NK010(tha)017:309: khugs nas gdab pa'i las bya'o //
NK010(tha)017:311: nyams par gyur pa'i dgra bo de //
NK010(tha)017:312: gang du bros pa'i gnas nas dgug /
NK010(tha)017:313: sprul pa mang po'i tshogs chen gyis //
NK010(tha)017:314: shig shig gul gul gnas pa ni //
NK010(tha)017:315: dper na grog tshang sbrul tshang bzhin //
NK010(tha)017:316: gnas pa zhabs kyi phur pa yis //
NK010(tha)017:317: sdong po bsgyur bzhin zhabs 'og na //
NK010(tha)017:318: mdangs bral gnas pa'i sbyor ba bya //
NK010(tha)017:320: gsum pa bsad pa'i thun gyi las sbyor la gsum /
NK010(tha)017:325: thun rdzas mang po thod par bsag /
NK010(tha)017:326: thod chen bzhi ru thun khrag go //
NK010(tha)017:331: khyi spyang la sogs pa'i thod par dam can so so'i thun rdzas gnad yig ltar 'du bya zhing /
NK010(tha)017:332: de yang thun sngags bris pa'i dar nag gis g.yogs la khri'u'i khar bzhag go //
NK010(tha)017:333: gnyis pa thun bsgrub pa ni /
NK010(tha)017:334: thams cad 'dus pa gnad la dbab //
NK010(tha)017:335: dpa' bo gcig pas dgra 'dzab bya //
NK010(tha)017:336: ma mo 'dus pa dam can la //
NK010(tha)017:337: gcun la dbab pa shes par bya //
NK010(tha)017:338: zhes pa'i don ni bzhi snying la ma mo'i thun sngags sdeb pa yin la /
NK010(tha)017:340: las kyi thun drug sngags la yang //
NK010(tha)017:341: nyin mo gtor la nub mo dril //
NK010(tha)017:342: gang bab dus su shes par bya //
NK010(tha)017:343: rtags myur srog bcad la sogs so //
NK010(tha)017:344: zhes pas nyin mo gtor te bzla ba ni /
NK010(tha)017:345: thun dang po sho na ma'i ngo bor bsgrub pa /
NK010(tha)017:346: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka
NK010(tha)017:347: tam ka ye h+aum ma ma pa shi ku ru
NK010(tha)017:348: ma tam nya che ge mo bla la thun /
NK010(tha)017:349: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:350: ces bzlas pas thun rdzas sho na ma bzhi'i ngo
NK010(tha)017:351: bor gyur pa las nad mtshon khro chung gi tsh+wa
NK010(tha)017:352: tsh+wa 'phros / gzas po'i snying ga nas btab bla
NK010(tha)017:353: bsad mdangs phrog nas nya bo la bstim pa ni
NK010(tha)017:355: khrag dug nad du gyur pa yis //
NK010(tha)017:356: dgra bo rims nad thebs pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)017:357: mdangs dang phral bar rab tu bsam //
NK010(tha)017:358: drag po'i dam rdzas thun phab pas //
NK010(tha)017:359: khro bor gyur pas bsad par bsam //
NK010(tha)017:360: de yang bar bar phyag rgya can //
NK010(tha)017:364: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh dza
NK010(tha)017:365: ye bi dza ye ka ra i nan che ge
NK010(tha)017:367: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:369: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh a
NK010(tha)017:370: tsi te a pa ra tsit+ta d+ha ti ma ma
NK010(tha)017:371: karma che ge mo bla la thun /
NK010(tha)017:372: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:374: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ma
NK010(tha)017:375: ra s+ya na pra marta na ye shi kram ka
NK010(tha)017:376: ra m+aa ra ya che ge mo bla la thun
NK010(tha)017:377: / sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:379: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka
NK010(tha)017:380: tam ka ye h+aum ma ma pa shi ku ru
NK010(tha)017:381: ma tam nya dza ye bi dza ye ka ra
NK010(tha)017:382: i nan / a tsi te a pa ra tsit+ta
NK010(tha)017:383: d+ha ti ma ma karma ma ra s+ya na pra
NK010(tha)017:384: marta na ye shi kram ka ra m+aa ra ya
NK010(tha)017:385: i nan / thun / sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)017:392: tha ma grangs bsnyen 'bum phrag gcig bazla'o //
NK010(tha)017:394: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos //
NK010(tha)017:395: byang chub mchog tu dus gsum rgyal ba'i rig 'dzin
NK010(tha)017:396: bdag cag gnod cing gdug pa'i bdud dang bar du
NK010(tha)017:397: dngos grub 'phrog cing khro bo chen po'i yud tsam
NK010(tha)017:398: gyis ni mngon spyod tshul bzhin lus ngag rdul du
NK010(tha)017:399: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)017:401: gsum pa bsad pa'am bsgrub pa chen po ni /
NK010(tha)017:402: ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa gzhung bsrang la de'i
NK010(tha)017:403: khong khrar gtong ba phal gyis mi rig pa'i man
NK010(tha)017:404: ngag yin te / gab sngags ming rus thabs sngags chen //
NK010(tha)017:405: ngan sngags 'dus pas bsgrub chen po //
NK010(tha)017:406: bsad par bya ba'i rim pa yin //
NK010(tha)017:407: zhes pas thun gyi bsgrub pa rdzogs rjes lha dang
NK010(tha)017:408: dbral ba nas smyo ru gzhug pa'i bar ngan sngags
NK010(tha)017:409: nye bar bsnyen pa bzhin la /
NK010(tha)017:410: phur gdab dang bsad gris gtub /
NK010(tha)017:411: rjes su thun gyis bsad pa'i sngags khong khrar btang ste /
NK010(tha)017:412: bsad pa thun gyi dmod mo yin //
NK010(tha)017:413: gab sngags thabs dang shes rab dang //
NK010(tha)017:414: thun dang ngan sngags khong khrar btang //
NK010(tha)017:416: de yang sngags kyi mtshon cha ni thun gyi las yin pas na /
NK010(tha)017:417: gab sngags them par bcas pa la //
NK010(tha)017:418: m+aa ra ya bcug bzlas pa bya //
NK010(tha)017:419: lcags kyi 'khor lo rab bskor bas //
NK010(tha)017:420: dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcad par bsam //
NK010(tha)017:422: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka
NK010(tha)017:423: tam ka ye ma ma pa shi ku ru ma
NK010(tha)017:424: tam nya dza ye bi dza ye ka ra i
NK010(tha)017:425: nan / a tsi te a pa ra tsi te
NK010(tha)017:426: d+ha ti ma ma karma ra s+ya na pra marta
NK010(tha)017:427: nan / na ye / sh+ri kram ka ra che
NK010(tha)017:428: ge mo m+aa ra ya sarba big nan bam h+aum
NK010(tha)017:429: nan / na ye / phata / dmigs pa ni /
NK010(tha)017:430: lha rnams drag por nges bsam la //
NK010(tha)017:431: yang sprul sum sprul mang po yis //
NK010(tha)017:432: shes pa ling+ga la zhugs bsad //
NK010(tha)017:433: bar bar thal mo dmod pa bya //
NK010(tha)017:435: bar du thun rnams brab pas yang //
NK010(tha)017:436: thod chen nang du nges pa ste //
NK010(tha)017:437: las kyi thun drug sngags kyis btab //
NK010(tha)017:438: dam can mang pos bsad par bsam //
NK010(tha)017:439: gtod cing stob cing za bar brtag /
NK010(tha)017:441: de ltar na ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa'i dus
NK010(tha)017:442: na phung po mthar byed thun gyi las yod na
NK010(tha)017:443: 'di'i dgos pa ci yin snyam na /
NK010(tha)017:444: 'di ni dam can nye bar bsnyen pa dang 'brel
NK010(tha)017:445: ba'i bsad pa thun mong ma yin pa khong khrar
NK010(tha)017:446: sdeb pa'i tshul / las kyi thun sngags bsad pa dang //
NK010(tha)017:447: rtags 'byin lhag pa lha yi dmod //
NK010(tha)017:448: srog gi chad pa thun gyi sngags //
NK010(tha)017:449: sngags drug phyin yod bya ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)017:450: khong khrar btang bas las myur bshad //
NK010(tha)017:451: ces pa'i man ngag yin no //
NK010(tha)017:452: de ltar bsgrub pa'i thun gyi lhag ma khrag sna dang bsres nas zor du 'phen pa'ang /
NK010(tha)017:453: 'phar ba'i thod par dam rdzas dang //
NK010(tha)017:454: khrag bcas gnas la zor du 'phang //
NK010(tha)017:456: wa thod nang du bse byang ni //
NK010(tha)017:457: dmar po bcug la phur pas mnan //
NK010(tha)017:458: khyi thod kha la me 'bar te //
NK010(tha)017:459: rdzas rnams sbyin bsreg bya ba yang //
NK010(tha)017:460: klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK010(tha)017:461: spyang thod kha la ling+ga dang //
NK010(tha)017:462: gtor ma lha la bstab pa bya //
NK010(tha)017:463: mnan pa lung gsum mdo ru nges //
NK010(tha)017:464: de ltar rab tu byas pa yis //
NK010(tha)017:465: rdo rje'i brag kyang 'jig gyur na //
NK010(tha)017:466: gzugs can rnams la smos ci dgos //
NK010(tha)017:467: zhes dam can spyi dril gyi sgrub thabs las bshad do //
NK010(tha)017:469: gshin rje grub nas 'khor lo bskor //
NK010(tha)017:470: ma mo grub nas zor thun 'phang //
NK010(tha)017:471: rgyal po grub nas mnan pa bya //
NK010(tha)017:472: phur pa grub nas gdab las bya //
NK010(tha)017:474: de'i don bstan pa dang sems can bsrung ba'i don
NK010(tha)017:475: du nyams pa bdun la dmigs pa las gzhan du
NK010(tha)017:477: dpyangs thag chad pa thugs rje yis //
NK010(tha)017:478: bzung na nges par bstan pa yin //
NK010(tha)017:479: nyams pa bdun las gzhan du min //
NK010(tha)017:480: zhes gsungs na rang dgar las sbyor dang mthu gtad
NK010(tha)017:481: la dga' ba ni rang rgyud kyi sdom pa 'jig
NK010(tha)017:482: cing bsod nams nyams pa'i rgyur gyur pas thog mar
NK010(tha)017:483: 'bras bu la bar du gcod pa'i rgyu'i r+au tra
NK010(tha)017:484: tshar bcad nas / gdod ma'i lam gyi r+au tra tshar gcod pa'i thabs la mkhas pa dgos te /
NK010(tha)017:485: rgyu yi r+au tras 'bras bu dang //
NK010(tha)017:486: lam gyi r+au tras bdag nyid phung //
NK010(tha)017:487: dug lnga'i nges pa rab shes bya //
NK010(tha)017:488: lam gyi r+au tra brnag pa ni //
NK010(tha)017:489: skye bo nyams pa can de spyir //
NK010(tha)017:491: thabs la mkhas pa'i rgyu yi gtso bo yang /
NK010(tha)017:492: gzhi ni snying rjes bzung ba dang //
NK010(tha)017:493: rtsa ba byang sems rtogs pa dang //
NK010(tha)017:494: thag ni lta bas bcad pa dang //
NK010(tha)017:495: la ni spyod pas dor ba dang //
NK010(tha)017:496: dbang ni dam tshig sgrol bas te //
NK010(tha)017:497: ngo bo nges tshig dbye shes na //
NK010(tha)017:498: gang byas sangs rgyas 'grub par nges //
NK010(tha)017:500: de bas na phur pa'i ngo bo byang chub kyi
NK010(tha)017:501: sems rin po che yin pas de mngon du byed
NK010(tha)017:502: pa'i thabs stod las byang chub bsgrub pa'i lam yin
NK010(tha)017:503: na lha bsnyen them tshad kyi smad las nges par
NK010(tha)017:505: byang chub bsgrub pa'i lam gyi bar gcod zhi ba
NK010(tha)017:506: la dmigs nas dam can nye bar bsnyen par 'dod
NK010(tha)017:507: na brub khung la sogs pa'i bcas rnams bor la
NK010(tha)017:508: / gtor ma dang mthun rdzas la brten nas bzhi
NK010(tha)017:509: snying dril ba'i bzlas pa mdun phrag la sogs pa'i
NK010(tha)017:510: mthar tshogs tha ma dang 'brel bar zan ling la
NK010(tha)017:511: gdab kha drug gi las thun mong ba bstab pa
NK010(tha)017:513: bal mo la sogs rtags byung nas //
NK010(tha)017:514: dngos grub blangs pas nus pa thob //
